1
00:00:03,250 --> 00:00:05,291
[ Tsubaki sneezes ]

2
00:00:05,375 --> 00:00:07,458
[ Sniffles ]

3
00:00:07,541 --> 00:00:08,916
Boy:
Tsubaki caught a cold?

4
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:11,708
That she-gorilla who wears
shorts all year long?

5
00:00:11,791 --> 00:00:13,625
Girl:
She sneezes funny.

6
00:00:13,708 --> 00:00:15,416
We're already infected!

7
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:16,875
-We need a medic!
-Run!

8
00:00:16,958 --> 00:00:18,541
Girl: She's gonna
gorillafy us!

9
00:00:18,625 --> 00:00:20,500
Tsubaki: Who are you calling
a gorilla, you little twerps?

10
00:00:20,583 --> 00:00:22,333
Kid:
It's on the warpath!

11
00:00:23,250 --> 00:00:24,583
[ Sneezes ]

12
00:00:24,666 --> 00:00:26,583
[ Sneezes ]

13
00:00:26,666 --> 00:00:28,083
[ Sneezes ]

14
00:00:34,375 --> 00:00:36,166
Kousei: Here.
Have some lemonade.

15
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:37,500
Huh? What are you doing?

16
00:00:37,583 --> 00:00:40,125
Vitamin C's good to take
when you have a cold.

17
00:00:40,208 --> 00:00:41,416
My mom told me so.

18
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:44,166
Yeah? Well, I don't have a cold,
so there.

19
00:00:44,250 --> 00:00:45,958
Gorillas are healthy
all the time.

20
00:00:46,041 --> 00:00:48,125
You're not a gorilla
at all, Tsubaki.

21
00:00:48,208 --> 00:00:49,291
Huh?

22
00:00:49,375 --> 00:00:51,916
You're a human.
A human girl.

23
00:00:54,208 --> 00:00:55,541
[ Grunts ]

24
00:00:55,625 --> 00:00:57,166
[ Gasps ]

25
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:58,458
Vitamin C!

26
00:00:58,541 --> 00:01:00,000
Whoa!

27
00:01:00,083 --> 00:01:03,291
<i>[COALAMODE.'S</i>
<i>"Nanairo Symphony"]</i>

28
00:01:03,375 --> 00:01:06,291
♪♪

29
00:01:06,375 --> 00:01:12,791
[ Singing in Japanese ]

30
00:01:12,875 --> 00:01:15,291
